data.description: This almost NEW energy-efficient home is the Verona floor plan from Meritage Homes. Single story 3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths and a 2 car garage. The expansive breakfast bar makes a great place to catch up after a busy day. Walk-in closets throughout solve storage challenges. Convenient to shopping, outdoor fun, and quick access to I10, I410, I35 and BAMC. Easy commute to Randolph AFB. This home is still covered through the Builders Warranty. Video and 3D Walkthrough link also available!
